OL,3,CMan in custody after teenage girl
OL,4,Ctaken at knifepoint from Altrincham
OL,5,Cstreet
OL,7,FA teenage girl was bundled into a
OL,8,Fvehicle in a 'random' suspected
OL,9,Fabduction in Altrincham.JThe 15 year
OL,10,Fold reported being threatened with a
OL,11,Fknife during the seven-hour ordeal.
OL,13,FA man's been arrested following the
OL,14,Fincident in Bowdon.
OL,16,FShe was snatched on Monday evening
OL,17,F(May 18) and found in the early hours
OL,18,Fof Tuesday morning (May 19) in a hotel
OL,19,Fcar park in Knutsford, Cheshire.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
