PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779311467
OL,3,CMan in custody after teenage girl
OL,4,Ctaken at knifepoint from Altrincham
OL,5,Cstreet
OL,7,FIt's understood the victim was forced
OL,8,Finto a vehicle on Bradgate Road,
OL,9,FBowdon, at around 7pm as she walked
OL,10,Falone. She was reported missing at
OL,11,Faround 9pm.
OL,13,FPolice issued an alert for a specific
OL,14,Fvehicle after a witness was able to
OL,15,Freport the registration plate having
OL,16,Fheard the girl's screams.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
