OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779311467
OL,3,CMan in custody after teenage girl
OL,4,Ctaken at knifepoint from Altrincham
OL,5,Cstreet
OL,7,FCheshire cops found the vehicle on a
OL,8,Fcar park at the Cottons Hotel and Spa
OL,9,Fin the early hours. The teenager was
OL,10,Finside and a man was arrested at the
OL,11,Fscene.
OL,13,FIn a statement, Greater Manchester
OL,14,FPolice said: "Officers working
OL,15,Falongside Cheshire Police have
OL,16,Farrested a man on suspicion of
OL,17,Fabduction after a teenage girl was
OL,18,Freported missing on Monday 18 May in
OL,19,FAltrincham.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
