OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779311467
OL,3,CMan in custody after teenage girl
OL,4,Ctaken at knifepoint from Altrincham
OL,5,Cstreet
OL,7,F"A 56yearold man was arrested in the
OL,8,Fearly hours of 19 May and remains in
OL,9,Fcustody for further questioning.
OL,11,F"Specialist officers are supporting
OL,12,Fthe girl and her family. There is no
OL,13,Fwider risk to the public. Further
OL,14,Fupdates will be provided when
OL,15,Fappropriate."
OL,17,FGreater Manchester Police said the man
OL,18,Farrested was a white male.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
