FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779311467
OL,3,CMan in custody after teenage girl
OL,4,Ctaken at knifepoint from Altrincham
OL,5,Cstreet
OL,7,FDetectives have been granted an
OL,8,Fextension to keep the suspect in
OL,9,Fcustody for further questioning.
OL,11,FIt is understood the incident is being
OL,12,Ftreated as random and the teenager is
OL,13,Fnot known to the suspect.
OL,15,FPolice are urging anyone who may have
OL,16,Fwitnessed the incident or has any
OL,17,Ffootage from the area to contact them.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
